Package: capivara
Type: Package
Title: Decomposition and Analysis of IFU Data Cubes
Version: 0.3.0
Imports: FITSio, dplyr, fastcluster, ggplot2, gridExtra, matrixStats, patchwork, readr, reshape2, RANN, Rcpp, scales, spectropath, tidyr, viridis, yaml
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: torch, EBImage, imager, knitr, minpack.lm, rmarkdown
Remotes:
    RafaelSdeSouza/spectropath
Author: Rafael S. de Souza
Maintainer: Rafael S. de Souza <rd23aag@herts.ac.uk>
Description: The 'capivara' package provides tools for spectral segmentation
    and analysis of Integral Field Unit (IFU) data cubes. It includes
    missing-data-aware exact clustering, sparse-Ward large-cube clustering,
    Sagui-style white-light starlet masks,
    variance-aware cluster summaries, and signal-to-noise-guided component
    selection for astronomy workflows.
